  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Preparing for a no deal Brexit if you provide telecoms services
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Use our checklist to understand what you need to do to prepare for no deal Brexit  if you provide telecoms services.</p>

  </div>
</div>

